column1: #Text=Panama-flagged ship hijacked off Somali coast by pirates
#Text=Suspected Somali pirates have hijacked the MV Al Khaliq , a Panama -flagged ship , off the eastern coast of Africa on Thursday .
#Text=International maritime officials said the ship was seized about 330 kilometers west of the Seychelles islands .
#Text=Officials reported that the ship is carrying 26 crew members — 24 Indians and two Burmese .
#Text=The Al Khaliq is the fourth ship Somali pirates have hijacked this month , and the third in the past week .
